     <section class="services">
        <h1>Services we offer</h1>
        <div class="services-box1">
            <h3><u>App Development</u></h3>
            <br>
            <p><i><u>Android Development:</u> Developing applications for Android devices using Java or Kotlin with tools like Android Studio. It involves designing, coding, testing, and deploying apps to the Google Play Store, ensuring compatibility across various Android versions and devices.

                <h4><u>iOS Development:</u></h4> Creating applications for Apple devices using Swift or Objective-C with Xcode. This process includes designing user interfaces, coding, testing, and deploying apps to the Apple App Store, ensuring seamless performance on iPhones and iPads.
                
                <h4><u>Cross-Platform Development:</u></h4> Building applications that run on multiple platforms (Android, iOS, etc.) using frameworks like React Native, Flutter, or Xamarin. This approach allows for sharing code across platforms, reducing development time and costs while maintaining a consistent user experience across different devices.</i></p>
        </div>
        <div class="services-box2">
            <h3><u>Web-Applications Development</u></h3>
            <br>
            <p><i>Web applications developed by Appzion leverage cutting-edge technologies to create dynamic and interactive experiences accessible via web browsers. These applications are designed to meet diverse client needs, offering scalability, cross-platform compatibility, and robust security features. With a focus on user-centric design and seamless functionality, Appzion's web applications empower businesses to reach their audience effectively on any device with internet connectivity. Our comprehensive development process ensures reliable performance, efficient maintenance, and continuous support to enhance client satisfaction and business success.</i></p>
        </div>
        <br>
        <div class="services-box3">
            <h3><u>Artifical Intelligence</u></h3>
            <br>
